keyFacts: A meeting specifically about the 'Epstein Case' with defense attorneys was scheduled for June 26, 2007.
The meeting was scheduled to last two hours (2:00 PM to 4:00 PM).
The calendar entry itself was created much later, on April 4, 2015, and modified in July 2015, indicating it was entered into a record-keeping system retrospectively.
